  "home.research.intro": [
    "site.popen",
      "My technical background predates my infrastructure and HPC work. Prior to moving into systems engineering and infrastructure work, I worked in ",
      "chemistry, conducting polymers, intelligent materials, supramolecular systems, biomaterials, and electrochemical composites. Although my career ",
      "trajectory ultimately shifted toward large-scale systems engineering and operational infrastructure, the scientific and experimental disciplines ",
      "developed during this period strongly influenced my later engineering philosophy.",
    "site.pclose",
    "site.br",
    "site.popen",
      "Research work included natural product biosynthesis, conducting polymer-hydrogel composites, electrochemical systems, responsive materials, and ",
      "intelligent biomaterials, resulting in multiple peer-reviewed publications and conference papers.",
